	<p:release projectid="tools.pdt" version="2.1" />
	<p:introduction>
		<p>The PDT project provides a PHP Development Tools framework for the Eclipse platform. This project encompasses all development components necessary to develop PHP and facilitate extensibility. It leverages the existing Web Tools Platform (PDT) and Dynamic Languages Toolkit (DLTK) in providing developers with PHP capabilities.</p>
	</p:introduction>
	<p:release_deliverables>
		<p>
		<ul>
		<li>PDT runtime package</li>
		<li>PDT SDK Package</li>
		<li>PDT Automated Test Package</li>
		<li>The Eclipse IDE for PHP Developers package</li>
			</ul>
		</p>
	</p:release_deliverables>
